Author: StressedCookie
Text: Whenever I see a nice snack or food I find fault in it: that has sugar, carbs, it has dairy, that's fried, or that doesn't have a nutrition label. It helps.

Author: CaptainMyCaptainRise
Text: My brain does this every time I knock something over, like 'hey if you were skinny you wouldn't have knocked over the mug of hot water, followed by 'well no eating for me'
